name: Angelcat and Friends Collection - Chase Chick
description:
Angel Cat and Friends is about Cheonsa the Cat, an angel cat sent to earth to help fellow animals do good deeds. To disguise herself and do her mission, Cheonsa runs Coffee Cat, a café that caters to all animals in town. Her most frequent customers are Danny Dog, Rita Rabbit, Paulie Penguin, Chase Chick, Owen Owl and Barry Bear. Each of them has his/her own likes and dislikes as well as good and bad traits. With her yummy food and drinks, little pieces of advice and some help with their needs, Cheonsa inspires them to become better versions of themselves. This NFT is one of Cheonsa's friends and café customers, Chase Chick.

Chase Chick is a young programming student who likes playing games and all things tech-related. He often goes to the café when he plays online games. There, he doesn’t need to worry about his meals because he just has to order them. Being the youngest of them all, he loves to play pranks, but he is patient in teaching his friends about technology.
